Usage:	update [-h] [-i] [-y] [-?] [--help] [--no-dist]

Makes complete update. Requires root privileges.

Options:
 -h,-?,--help	display this help and exit
 -i		make an update interactively
 -m, --menu	open GUI Update Menu
 -y		make an update with no questions (default)
 --no-dist	make an upgrade using: apt-get upgrade, not apt-get dist-upgrade

Exit status:
 0	if OK
 1	if the argument is not recognised
